 "components": {
  "instruction": "You are given a text input describing a customer issue or query related to banking, payments, or financial services. Your task is to assign this input to one of the following predefined categories that best matches the main topic or concern described in the text:\n\n- automatic_top_up\n- balance_not_updated_after_bank_transfer\n- beneficiary_not_allowed\n- cancel_transfer\n- card_payment_fee_charged\n- card_payment_not_recognised\n- declined_cash_withdrawal\n- exchange_rate\n- exchange_via_app\n- failed_transfer\n- get_disposable_virtual_card\n- get_physical_card\n- passcode_forgotten\n- pending_top_up\n- pending_transfer\n- receiving_money\n- reverted_card_payment?\n- top_up_by_cash_or_cheque\n- top_up_reverted\n- topping_up_by_card\n- transfer_fee_charged\n- transfer_into_account\n- transfer_timing\n- verify_my_identity\n- verify_source_of_funds\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. Read the input text carefully to determine the primary issue or request. This may include information about specific features (like cards, transfers, top-ups), transaction statuses, or problems encountered by the user.\n2. Match the input text to the single most appropriate category from the list above. Consider any domain-specific meaning — for example, \"get_physical_card\" refers to requests or issues obtaining a physical debit or credit card, while \"passcode_forgotten\" specifically relates to trouble remembering or accessing an account passcode, not the physical delivery of a PIN or card.\n3. Do NOT invent new categories or output anything other than the exact category name provided.\n4. If the text could potentially fit several categories, select the most specific one that directly addresses the user's main problem as described.\n5. Your output should be only the category name, with no extra words or explanation.\n\nExample:\n\nInput text: \"I've been waiting ages and my PIN hasn't gotten here.\"\n\nOutput: get_physical_card\n\nIn the example, even though \"PIN\" is referenced, the main issue is the non-arrival of the user's physical card (often PIN mailers accompany cards or relate to card delivery issues), so the correct category is \"get_physical_card\" and not \"passcode_forgotten\".\n\nRefer to the category list and examples when making your decision to help prevent miscategorization."
 },
